---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sponsors | Cloud Identity Summit">
    <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 w-full flex-grow overflow-hidden">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm mb-3 block">Our Partners</span>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Sponsors</h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Without the support of our incredible partners, this community event would not be possible.</p>
        </div>
        
        <section class="mb-24 relative">
            <div class="absolute -inset-x-4 -inset-y-4 z-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500/10 to-transparent blur-2xl rounded-[3rem] opacity-50 pointer-events-none"></div>
            
            <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
                <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-yellow-500 flex-1"></div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-center px-4">Gold</h2>
                <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-yellow-500 flex-1"></div>
            </div>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative z-10">
    <a href="https://www.adesso.de/en" target="_blank" class="group relative bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-yellow-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-yellow-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div class="h-16 mb-6 flex items-center">
            <img src="/images/sponsors/adesso.svg" alt="adesso SE Logo" class="h-full w-auto object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">adesso SE</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm flex-grow">Business success is the result of innovative ideas, forward-looking strategies and perfectly tailored IT solutions. With a team of around 6.300 employees on 56 sites, we are one of the leading IT service providers in the German-speaking area.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-yellow-500 text-sm font-semibold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all -translate-x-4 group-hover:translate-x-0 duration-300">
            Visit Website <span class="ml-2">→</span>
        </div>
    </a>

    <a href="https://www.glueckkanja.com/en" target="_blank" class="group relative bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-yellow-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-yellow-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div class="h-16 mb-6 flex items-center">
            <img src="/images/sponsors/glueckkanja.png" alt="glueckkanja AG Logo" class="h-full w-auto object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">glueckkanja AG</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm flex-grow">glueckkanja, a renowned Cloud Managed Service Provider, is a Microsoft partner offering comprehensive cloud solutions. With a unified blueprint approach, glueckkanja uses Infrastructure as Code to transition and support customer infrastructures.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-yellow-500 text-sm font-semibold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all -translate-x-4 group-hover:translate-x-0 duration-300">
            Visit Website <span class="ml-2">→</span>
        </div>
    </a>

    <a href="https://www.token2.com/" target="_blank" class="group relative bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-yellow-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-yellow-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div class="h-16 mb-6 flex items-center">
            <img src="/images/sponsors/token2.png" alt="TOKEN2 Logo" class="h-full w-auto object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">TOKEN2</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm flex-grow">Token2 is a cybersecurity company specializing in multifactor authentication. Alongside legacy OTP-based hardware tokens and standard FIDO2 keys, Token2 offers the innovative PIN+ series.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-yellow-500 text-sm font-semibold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all -translate-x-4 group-hover:translate-x-0 duration-300">
            Visit Website <span class="ml-2">→</span>
        </div>
    </a>

    <a href="https://tenantmanager.com/" target="_blank" class="group relative bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-yellow-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-yellow-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-yellow-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div class="h-16 mb-6 flex items-center">
            <img src="/images/sponsors/softwarecentral.png" alt="SoftwareCentral Logo" class="h-full w-auto object-contain" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-yellow-400 transition-colors">SoftwareCentral</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm flex-grow">SoftwareCentral’s Tenant Manager enhances Microsoft Intune with enterprise-grade governance, automates change controls, and delivers granular oversight across multi-tenant environments.</p>
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-yellow-500 text-sm font-semibold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all -translate-x-4 group-hover:translate-x-0 duration-300">
            Visit Website <span class="ml-2">→</span>
        </div>
    </a>
</div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-24 relative">
             <div class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-4 mb-10">
                <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-slate-400 flex-1"></div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-widest text-center px-4">Silver</h2>
                <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-slate-400 flex-1"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-slate-900/40 border border-slate-800 border-dashed rounded-3xl p-12 text-center">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-slate-800/50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                    <span class="text-2xl">🤝</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Become a Silver Sponsor</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6">No Silver Sponsors yet. Secure your spot and support the community.</p>
                <a href="/call-for-sponsors" class="bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 text-white px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-semibold transition inline-block border border-slate-700">View Sponsorship Packages</a>
            </div>
        </section>

<section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Bronze Sponsors</h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 relative z-10">
        <a href="https://msc-cyberguard.de/" target="_blank" class="group relative bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 hover:border-orange-500/50 hover:bg-slate-800/80 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl group-hover:bg-orange-500/20 transition-all duration-500"></div>
            
            <div class="h-16 mb-6 flex items-center">
                <img src="/images/sponsors/msc-cyber-guard-logo-resized.png" alt="MSC Cyber Guard Logo" class="h-full w-auto object-contain" />
            </div>
            
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 group-hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">MSC Cyber Guard</h3>
            
            <p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed text-sm flex-grow">
                As a trusted partner in the field of information security, we are committed to providing companies with comprehensive support and protection. We not only contribute our in-depth expertise and many years of experience in the areas of Microsoft infrastructure, Active Directory and Entra ID security to customer-specific projects, but also develop customized solutions for each individual challenge. Our primary goal is to continuously improve security in corporate environments and establish effective preventive measures. With our dedicated team of security experts, we face the ever-changing security challenges of the digital world.
            </p>
            
            <div class="mt-6 flex items-center text-orange-500 text-sm font-semibold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all -translate-x-4 group-hover:translate-x-0 duration-300">
                Visit Website <span class="ml-2">→</span>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

    </main>
</Layout>